{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/lindo.gif?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bagdex is a turn-based combat base building RPG featuring fantastic creatures - the <strong>Bagmons</strong>! Explore the vast world of Brasilis, build and customize <strong>your own base</strong>, discover over <strong>160 unique creatures</strong> and train them to win <strong>battles</strong> and face the mysteries of this world!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/title01_en.png?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Choose</strong> your Starting Village and <strong>explore the five regions of the world your way</strong>! Brasilis is a land full of mysteries and history, with dozens of eccentric trainers to challenge, mysterious Ruins to explore and a <strong>great secret</strong> to uncover!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/01_3.gif?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/title02_en.png?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Manage the Training Center - a <strong>fully customizable base</strong> to train your team, increase the <strong>friendship level</strong> with your Bagmons, <strong>cultivate your farm</strong>, prepare <strong>typical recipes</strong> discovered on your travels, <strong>fish</strong> and, of course, <strong>decorate</strong> it however you want!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/gif_ct_1.gif?t=1738754158\" />\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/title03_en.png?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight and ally with over <strong>160 species</strong>, distributed among 20 different Essential Types! <strong>Evolve</strong> your Bagmons into more powerful forms and improve their attributes. Plus, all Bagmons have alternate variations: <strong>Sparkling</strong> and the rare <strong>Radiant</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/02_3.gif?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/title04_en.png?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face opponents in strategic combat, with <strong>hundreds of unique moves and passive abilities</strong>! A good strategy is essential to win challenging battles - test your skills in the Brasilis Network Studios and against the infamous Tru-K Crew!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/3_02.gif?t=1738754158\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3361480/extras/title05_en.png?t=1738754158\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Breathtaking 2.5D cartoon art</strong> that stands out</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Original nostalgic soundtrack</strong> to set the vibe</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>PvP ba